harapan sama sekali.

27
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:33,520
Sulaman ini sungguh bagus.

28
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:43,360
Lian, hari sudah gelap,

29
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,960
